{
  "stem": "17761.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 157.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I liked to watch my father and then later to join my father and my grandfather who were standing in the dining room having a book of notes, of musical notes of different prayers, singing those notes.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's the way I still know [INAUDIBLE] until nowadays, despite the fact I-- I am not a musician.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We liked to have guests in the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then we did all kind of things that my parents asked us to.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But mostly our life turned around our studies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that I had no plans, simply.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't think to it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was so involved in the actual life that to plan what will be when I'll be-- I assume that I was almost sure that I'm going to end up something similar to my father.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I didn't plan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have to-- you are talking about someone who is just at the end of [INAUDIBLE] I was just touching adolescence, so these-- [DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, we had negative relationships.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For instance, I used to visit my grandparents' parents in Balaceana.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one of my relatives was a strong guy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was considered to be the third strongest guy in the village.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I don't know by what criteria.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we liked to go with him, because all the [NON-ENGLISH] were afraid of him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when they started with us, he used to run after them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They used to run away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I had all kinds of such incidents with [NON-ENGLISH] in the village who tried, some of them, to pull my payot-- I had payot at that time-- or just to call me names or just to chase me or just to run after me.",
      "word_count": 45
    }
  ],
